{"tid":219681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［又係港女］兩港女立山黑部訂房no show驚動日警上山尋人 入境處證虛驚一場","createTime":"2017-04-27T11:19:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T11:02:11.000Z","uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":142,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d8d9ff5338a4f31203fd218f960ed3c31e7c915d","tid":219681,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:19:39.000Z","msg":"日本傳媒今日報道，指兩名年約三十多歲的香港女子，原定昨晚入住立山黑部一間旅館，但兩人一直未有現身，由於擔心二人是否在雪山上失蹤，旅館安全起見於是報警。日本警方今早開始更派人上山搜索。<br />\n<br />\n不過，入境處傍晚回覆本報稱已聯絡上兩人，證實她們安全無恙。入境處表示，已即時透過外交部駐港特派員公署及中國駐名古屋總領事館了解情況。入境處亦已主動聯繫當事人，得悉二人現正身處安全地方，並向他們提供適切意見。處方重申，在外香港居民如需協助，可致電入境處「協助在外香港居民小組」的24小時求助熱線，電話：（852）1868。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170427&amp;guid=56622262&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170427%26guid%3D56622262%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=b9b26aab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170427%26guid%3D56622262%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=2d80b1f0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170427&amp;guid=56622262&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你老味又係港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n影鳩衰晒香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bbea0d9a4ca8e7390f2c39374478c9ea2a7849a","tid":219681,"uid":51978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:21:25.000Z","msg":"屌 港女 = 無腦 + 無品"},{"pid":"5866597c0298e59bacd132f32f944dbee10f2d68","tid":219681,"uid":45232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:23:30.000Z","msg":"30幾歲人都咁無交帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d463c1b27f57d6dd109f6c10f0f5f3