img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSend email比香港旅行社已經夠戇鳩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你理得人send比邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最後酒店係收到人地通知wo</blockquote><br />\n咪係， 上面果幾頁就係度屌人冇交帶話人自動缺席， 依家炒撚左車又話人好send 比邊個邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcddd335746e7307b78da9b82b02dd4b1d248020","tid":219681,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:03:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>&quot;報道指兩女原應在昨晚入住山莊內一間酒店，惟至昨晚9時30分仍未有現身，據職員指，酒店距離巴士站步程約30至40分鐘，當地正下雪，能見度欠佳，擔心兩人或在途中出事。亦有指兩女曾向旅行社傳電郵，聲稱因下雪，或未必能抵達酒店。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n點睇撞車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔理啦， 港女是原罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSend email比香港旅行社已經夠戇鳩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日月報話係send 比酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n　２６日夜、立山の山荘の従業員から「午後９時半を過ぎても宿泊予定の女性２人が到着していない」と警察に通報がありました。捜査関係者によりますと、２６日午後５時２２分に<span style=\"color: red;\">行方不明の２人から旅行代理店の担当者に「雪で道に迷って山荘にたどりつけない」というメールが届き</span>、それ以降は２人との連絡がとれていないということです。<br />\n<br />\n日本傳媒這樣說的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d3d662ada3cfc4bc41843723dc344369190024","tid":219681,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:07:43.000Z","msg":"當地傳媒報道，兩名年約34歲的女事主，同樣姓藍，原定昨晚抵達立山黑部入住當地旅館「雷鳥莊」，但兩人截至昨晚9時許仍未有現身，旅館為安全起見於是報警。報道指，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兩港女曾經在昨天黃昏時段發短訊予旅行Agent，稱未能如期抵達旅館，隨即完全失去聯絡</span>。由於擔心兩人於雪山迷路，日本警方派人今早開始上山搜索。<br />\n不過，入境處傍晚回覆本報稱已聯絡上兩人，證實她們安全無恙。據了解，兩人昨日失聯後，其實一直安全，只是沒有與旅館聯繫，結果惹來雪山失蹤驚魂。"},{"pid":"f1a91afa63fe6abbe397d4a397ffd6c8b850bf26","tid":219681,"uid":322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:08:36.000Z","msg":"叫唔叫撞車好"},{"pid":"e6c5c4e797d6dea0d325fb79497314aa98b98669","tid":219681,"uid":108022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:09:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D旅館都幾有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日本人(做野mode)係好有信用，唔通知又失約係好羞家既事，邊會諗到世上會有D咁既奇人異士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3403e597be98e489de1bc9c0879498c38e3090","tid":219681,"uid":11914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:10:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫唔叫撞車好</blockquote><br />\n叫， 點解唔叫<br />\n你睇下第一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3f0e88a9a1ad2a32512b826c144778f550e7c83","tid":219681,"uid":8922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:12:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>叫唔叫撞車好</blockquote><br />\n叫， 點解唔叫<br />\n你睇下第一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓上都仲有人撞緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da20a46d12d580fa9668605fa6c1fec8c5e257e","tid":219681,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:12:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>叫唔叫撞車好</blockquote><br />\n叫， 點解唔叫<br />\n你睇下第一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓上都仲有人撞緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n直炒埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1beb0c3a36457e39fd440f75f6d2bab750d6450e","tid":219681,"uid":76751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:17:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>叫唔叫撞車好</blockquote><br />\n叫， 點解唔叫<br />\n你睇下第一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><b